description: The deaths come after 37 residents of Abbotswood Nursing Home tested positive for the virus.
title: Coronavirus: Three Abbotswood Nursing Home residents die
title_page: Coronavirus: Three Abbotswood Nursing Home residents die - BBC News
maintext: It brings the total number of people to have died on the island after suffering Covid-19 to nine, while there have been some 300 positive cases.
